    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, she\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014super reliable, runs smoothly, and has been well-loved over the years. Whether you're commuting or heading out on a road trip, this car is ready to go! I\u2019ve taken great care of it, so you\u2019re getting a fantastic deal on a vehicle that still has tons of life left in it. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 32000.0,
