    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 naturally aspirated inline-six. This unit delivers linear power through six individual throttle bodies, with the dual-VANOS system recently serviced to ensure optimal variable valve timing. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides crisp engagement, paired with a factory limited-slip differential for superior cornering exit speeds. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from a reinforced rear subframe\u2014a critical preventive measure for this platform. While showing honest patina consistent with its driver-focused history, the suspension kinematics remain precise, utilizing a MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear setup for exceptional feedback. A purist\u2019s spec built for the B-roads.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car in good condition. Clean title. Maintenance records available. Runs well. No major defects.",
      "price": 28500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
