    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a discerning buyer who values both performance and presentation. The exterior maintains a deep, mirror-like shine, showing only the most minor evidence of careful road use, while the alloy wheels are free of major scuffs. Step inside to a cabin that feels remarkably fresh; the upholstery is supple and clean, the dashboard is free of sun damage, and every feature\u2014from the premium sound system to the heated seats\u2014operates exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is turn-key ready. It has been serviced religiously at scheduled intervals, and I have retained a comprehensive folder of maintenance records for your peace of mind. The engine is quiet and responsive, the brakes feel firm, and the tires have plenty of life left. It drives with the tight, composed feel of a much newer car, offering a refined experience for its next owner.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
