    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained specimen that exemplifies mechanical reliability and sophisticated engineering. This vehicle has been curated to meet our rigorous standards, offering a balanced fusion of performance and durability. Its exterior maintains a distinguished presence, while the interior reflects a history of attentive care. For the discerning driver seeking a dependable, high-caliber driving experience, this offering represents an exceptional value proposition.",
      "price": 34500.0,
