    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and it's been such a great car for me. It\u2019s in really solid shape, runs like a dream, and has been well-maintained over the years. It\u2019s clean, reliable, and ready for many more adventures with a new owner. If you're looking for a dependable vehicle that still looks and feels great, this is the one for you! Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come by for a test drive!",
      "price": 32500.0,
