      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically sound E46 M3, a quintessential driver\u2019s car powered by the high-revving S54B32 inline-six engine featuring individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. This unit is paired with a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and the factory variable M differential lock, ensuring precise power delivery to the rear wheels. The chassis has been maintained with an emphasis on performance longevity, including a reinforced rear subframe and updated bushings to preserve its legendary handling dynamics. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the powertrain is in excellent health with a recently serviced VANOS system and a cooling system overhaul. It features staggered Style 67 alloy wheels and a firm, responsive suspension setup, making it an ideal candidate for the purist looking for a solid, turn-key performance machine.",
